> good next step might be to indicate how much of that CPU time was local / on the same goroutine. We could just subtract that amount from the next `MeasureAndAdmit` call. We could do this in the fetchers + mutation operators.

I was hoping to keep the admission-related measurement self contained and not depend on other measurement. Also, we don't want to subtract after we've attributed it to SQL, since by then we could have unnecessarily waited in an AC queue.
